one_reviews_text: This is a great educational tool regarding acidification but it seems like it was created many years ago and never updated.

review_feedback: Sorry to hear that you're having difficulties with the sound. Our app should have sound and I am happy to help you troubleshoot this. Please ensure that you have your Rift set as the default output device. Thanks!
